WEBVTT

00:05.973 --> 00:07.207
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "WEEDS"...</i>

00:07.241 --> 00:09.576
I NEED A MIRACLE.
I NEED A MIRACLE!

00:09.610 --> 00:10.944
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

00:10.978 --> 00:12.913
I THINK GOD
WANTS HIM ALIVE.

00:12.946 --> 00:14.214
Nancy:
CAN I PLEASE HAVE MY MONEY?

00:14.248 --> 00:16.884
NO. AND I THINK YOU ABOUT
TO GIVE ME THEM DRUGS, TOO.

00:16.917 --> 00:17.918
FUCK YOU, LATRICE.

00:17.951 --> 00:19.052
YOU WORSE THAN I THOUGHT.

00:19.086 --> 00:20.754
PUT A BABY IN ME.

00:20.787 --> 00:21.955
COME ON, SHITHEAD.
GIVE ME YOUR SPERM.

00:21.989 --> 00:23.724
IT DOESN'T COST YOU
ANYTHING.
ALL RIGHT.

00:23.757 --> 00:24.825
[ Laughing ] WHAT?

00:24.858 --> 00:26.226
I LOVE COLLEGE SO MUCH.

00:26.260 --> 00:29.763
WHY DIDN'T ANYBODY TELL ME
HOW AWESOME COLLEGE IS?

00:29.796 --> 00:31.064
'CAUSE YOU WERE NEVER
GONNA GO.

00:31.098 --> 00:32.466
WE HAVE TO LEAVE SEATTLE.

00:32.499 --> 00:33.934
OKAY. WHY?

00:33.967 --> 00:35.636
WE'RE ON THE RUN NOW, HONEY.
IT'S WHAT WE DO.

00:35.669 --> 00:36.904
KIMMI...

00:36.937 --> 00:38.038
YEAH?

00:38.071 --> 00:40.040
CAN I BORROW YOUR CAR?
Nancy:
YOU GOT A CAR!

00:40.073 --> 00:41.575
YOU ARE THE HERO
OF THIS FAMILY!

00:41.608 --> 00:43.377
NO, I JUST BORROWED IT.

00:43.410 --> 00:46.046
SILAS, YOU'VE ONLY KNOWN HER
FOR A COUPLE OF DAYS,

00:46.079 --> 00:48.081
AND THIS IS CRISIS TIME HERE,
SO OPEN THE FUCKING TRUNK.

00:48.115 --> 00:49.716
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

00:49.750 --> 00:50.651
[ MUFFLED GRUNTING ]

00:50.684 --> 00:53.587
ANDY!
WE GOT TO GO, NOW!

00:53.620 --> 00:56.056
AAH! [ GRUNTS ]

00:56.089 --> 00:58.592
YOU RIPPED MY EAR.
NOW I CAN'T WEAR EARRINGS.

00:58.625 --> 01:01.795
Man: OPEN UP.
SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT.
ONE SECOND!

01:01.828 --> 01:03.297
HI.

01:03.330 --> 01:05.966
I'M WITH KING COUNTY
CHILD PROTECTIVE SERVICES.

01:05.999 --> 01:07.134
IS THERE A MALE INFANT
LIVING HERE?

01:07.167 --> 01:09.903
OH. HE PEED ON MY PEE.

01:09.937 --> 01:12.606
WE CROSSED STREAMS.

01:12.639 --> 01:13.841
THIS LOOKS WEIRD.

01:13.874 --> 01:14.975
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

01:15.008 --> 01:17.644
HELLO?
SHANE?

01:17.678 --> 01:19.813
MOM...

01:19.847 --> 01:20.981
THE FUCKERS GOT ME.

01:21.014 --> 01:23.150
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

01:36.997 --> 01:40.901
WHOSE BABY IS THIS
AND WHY DID YOU PEE ON IT?

01:40.934 --> 01:43.337
[ LAUGHS ]
NO. WE CROSSED STREAMS.

01:43.370 --> 01:44.905
IT'S ‐‐
OUR ‐‐ OUR PEE INTERSECTED.

01:44.938 --> 01:46.607
IT DID NOT GET ON THE BABY.

01:46.640 --> 01:49.276
MOST OF THE PEE
DID NOT GET ON THE BABY.

01:49.309 --> 01:53.547
LOOK, UM, WE ARE VERY CAPABLE
OF CREATING

01:53.580 --> 01:57.251
A NURTURING, INFANT‐FRIENDLY
ENVIRONMENT.

01:57.284 --> 01:59.987
THE ARROW IN THE CLOSET
IS PURELY DECORATIVE.

02:00.020 --> 02:03.924
THIS IS BABY AVI.
HE BELONGS TO MY SON, SHAWN.

02:03.957 --> 02:05.959
YOU SAID YOU DIDN'T HAVE
ANY KIDS.

02:05.993 --> 02:07.160
STEPSON. HE IS.

02:07.194 --> 02:09.029
I THOUGHT
YOU WEREN'T MARRIED.

02:09.062 --> 02:10.097
RIGHT.
NATHALIE!

02:10.130 --> 02:12.266
[ POUNDING ON DOOR ]

02:12.299 --> 02:14.501
ANSWER, ANSWER,
ANSWER, ANSWER.

02:15.969 --> 02:17.905
CESAR: Hello?
WHERE ARE YOU?

02:17.938 --> 02:21.408
BRING HIS SON.
I BRING YOUR SON.

02:21.441 --> 02:23.043
THEN WE TRADE.

02:23.076 --> 02:26.213
A shoe for a shoe.

02:27.915 --> 02:30.050
I WANT TO SPEAK TO SHANE
AGAIN.
No.

02:30.083 --> 02:31.251
TIME TO LISTEN.

02:31.285 --> 02:34.254
[ POUNDING CONTINUES ]
HANG ON.
FUCK!

02:35.956 --> 02:38.625
AAH! AAH!

02:38.659 --> 02:40.561
AAAH!

02:40.594 --> 02:42.663
YOU'RE TOO LOUD.

02:42.696 --> 02:44.198
KIMMI:
You're awesome!

02:44.231 --> 02:46.800
NO, YOU'RE AWESOME.

02:46.834 --> 02:48.068
MAN:
What up, faggot?!

02:48.101 --> 02:50.737
WHO WAS THAT?
Who do you think,
faggot?

02:50.771 --> 02:53.040
Now he's giving you
a lewd gesture.

02:53.073 --> 02:54.074
IT'S A GUY THING.

02:54.107 --> 02:55.909
TELL HIM,
UH, WHEN HE'S BACK,

02:55.943 --> 02:57.911
I'M GONNA KICK HIS ASS
IN "ULTIMATE."

02:57.945 --> 03:00.013
[ Chuckling ]
Right.

03:00.047 --> 03:01.715
Okay, pick me up at 6:00.

03:01.748 --> 03:02.749
[ Click ]

03:02.783 --> 03:05.953
CESAR:
Drive east on 90.

03:05.986 --> 03:08.121
I'LL CALL YOU BACK
IN 20 MINUTES.

03:08.155 --> 03:10.224
AND MAKE SURE
YOU PICK UP.

03:10.257 --> 03:13.060
OKAY. EAST ON 90.
OKAY.

03:13.093 --> 03:14.761
BITCH, YOU GONNA GET
YOUR TEETH BENT BACK.

03:14.795 --> 03:18.265
YEAH, MY SON'S BEEN KIDNAPPED.
CAN'T FIGHT WITH YOU RIGHT NOW.

03:23.103 --> 03:27.508
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

03:27.541 --> 03:29.743
WHY DID YOU GUYS BLOW TOWN
FOR SEATTLE?

03:29.776 --> 03:31.078
BETTER SCHOOLS.

03:31.111 --> 03:32.145
HE KILLED PILAR.

03:32.179 --> 03:34.515
OH, THE GUY
WHO REDID THE BATHROOM?

03:34.548 --> 03:35.749
NO.

03:35.782 --> 03:37.351
EVIL BRUJA.

03:37.384 --> 03:38.652
OH.

03:38.685 --> 03:40.787
[ STOMACH GROWLS ]

03:40.821 --> 03:43.023
GOT ANY FOOD?

03:43.056 --> 03:46.760
HEY, REMEMBER THAT TIME
THAT I BROUGHT YOU WITH ME

03:46.793 --> 03:48.595
TO COLLECT FROM THE GUY
WITH THE HAT

03:48.629 --> 03:51.031
AND THEN AFTER I KNEECAPPED HIM,
YOU STEPPED ON HIS HAT?

03:51.064 --> 03:52.933
YEAH.
GOOD TIMES.

03:52.966 --> 03:55.702
[ LAUGHS ]
GOOD TIMES.

03:57.271 --> 03:59.973
WOULD YOU REALLY PUT A BULLET
IN ME?

04:01.275 --> 04:02.609
Sí.

04:02.643 --> 04:04.578
[ SIGHS ]

04:04.611 --> 04:07.881
WOULD YOU JUST BREATHE ON ME
SO I COULD SMELL SOME FOOD?

04:07.915 --> 04:10.450
AND THEN THE TERMITES SURROUNDED
THE FOUNDATION

04:10.484 --> 04:11.518
AND DEVOURED THE PORCH,

04:11.552 --> 04:13.854
AND SO THAT'S WHY
WE'RE LIVING HERE NOW.

04:13.887 --> 04:17.991
WHERE'S THE BABY'S FATHER NOW?
SHAWN, IS IT?

04:18.025 --> 04:20.928
HE'S, UM...

04:20.961 --> 04:22.262
WHO ARE YOU?

04:22.296 --> 04:23.664
WHO THE FUCK
ARE YOU?

04:23.697 --> 04:25.299
OH!
OH, I MISS MEGAN.

04:32.806 --> 04:34.741
THIS IS MY OTHER SON,
MIKE.

04:34.775 --> 04:38.212
AND WE NEED TO BE SOMEWHERE
REALLY IMPORTANT RIGHT NOW.

04:38.245 --> 04:39.346
SO, IF WE COULD JUST...

04:39.379 --> 04:41.014
COME TO MY OFFICE
FOR A FOLLOW‐UP.

04:41.048 --> 04:43.016
WE'LL NEED TO SEE
SOME DOCUMENTATION.

04:43.050 --> 04:43.951
BRING THE FATHER.

04:43.984 --> 04:45.352
TOMORROW.

04:46.420 --> 04:48.322
TOMORROW.

04:52.726 --> 04:55.028
CALL ME.

04:55.062 --> 04:58.098
[ SIGHS ]
THAT WAS A CLOSE ONE.

04:58.131 --> 05:00.234
CESAR'S GOT SHANE.

05:02.035 --> 05:03.637
SON OF A BITCH.

05:03.670 --> 05:04.905
[ SIGHS ]

05:04.938 --> 05:06.440
[ Telephone ringing ]

05:06.473 --> 05:08.675
FEMALE VOICE: You've reached
the voice mailbox of...

05:08.709 --> 05:10.010
ESTEBAN: Esteban.

05:10.043 --> 05:12.112
FEMALE VOICE:
Please record your message.

05:12.145 --> 05:13.413
[ Beep ]
HI.

05:13.447 --> 05:15.849
UH, IT'S ME AGAIN.

05:15.883 --> 05:19.253
BOY, AM I SORRY
I IGNORED YOUR CALLS.

05:19.286 --> 05:23.123
UH, I SEE NOW THAT
THAT WAS REALLY WRONG.

05:23.156 --> 05:24.992
AND I'M SO, SO SORRY

05:25.025 --> 05:27.928
FOR NOT PICKING UP
THE PHONE

05:27.961 --> 05:29.663
AND TALKING TO YOU
DIRECTLY.

05:29.696 --> 05:32.099
[ RADIO TUNING ]
I'M SO SORRY.
IT WAS REALLY WRONG.

05:32.132 --> 05:33.634
[ RADIO SHUTS OFF ]
Sorry, sorry, sorry.

05:33.667 --> 05:35.769
Y‐YOU MUST HAVE FELT
AWFUL.

05:35.802 --> 05:40.007
UM, I'D LOVE TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT IT

05:40.040 --> 05:41.341
AND APOLOGIZE DIRECTLY.

05:41.375 --> 05:44.945
AND I'D ALSO REALLY LOVE
TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT SHANE.

05:44.978 --> 05:48.048
YOU KNEW THAT WAS GONNA GET
MY ATTENTION.

05:48.081 --> 05:49.850
BOY, YOU WERE RIGHT.
YOU GOT IT.

05:49.883 --> 05:52.853
[ AIR CONDITIONING BLOWS ]
KIDNAPPING
YOUR BABY BOY'S BROTHER!

05:52.886 --> 05:55.088
REALLY?!

05:55.122 --> 05:57.357
[ Loudly ] SOLID MOVE,
PADRE‐OF‐THE‐YEAR...
[ AIR CONDITIONING SHUTS OFF ]

05:57.391 --> 05:58.525
SHITTY FUCKER!

05:58.559 --> 06:01.595
YOU MACHO COWBOY, I‐‐

06:02.729 --> 06:04.932
...asshole.

06:04.965 --> 06:07.601
[ Normal voice ]
SO, UM...

06:07.634 --> 06:09.436
I HOPE TO HEAR
FROM YOU SOON.

06:09.469 --> 06:12.239
I'D ASK SHANE
HOW TO DISABLE THE CALLER I. D.,

06:12.272 --> 06:14.808
BUT ‐‐ OOPS ‐‐
HE'S BEEN KIDNAPPED.

06:14.842 --> 06:18.445
SO, UM,
PLEASE CALL THIS OFF.

06:18.478 --> 06:21.048
PLEASE CALL ME BACK.

06:21.081 --> 06:25.986
OKAY?
AND I'M ‐‐ I'M SORRY.

06:26.019 --> 06:27.988
[ BEEP ]

06:28.021 --> 06:30.924
WOULD IT BE WORTH,

06:30.958 --> 06:34.194
I DON'T KNOW,
HAVING A HYPOTHETICAL DISCUSSION

06:34.228 --> 06:38.532
ON WHAT WOULD HAPPEN
IF WE GAVE STEVIE ‐‐

06:38.565 --> 06:41.935
NO.
THAT'S INSANE.

06:41.969 --> 06:45.005
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
IS THAT MY MASCARA?

06:45.038 --> 06:47.741
WAR PAINT.
YOU'RE GONNA NEED BACKUP.

06:47.774 --> 06:49.376
YEAH, YOU'RE
NOT COMING WITH ME.

06:49.409 --> 06:51.111
OF COURSE
I'M COMING WITH YOU.

06:51.144 --> 06:53.247
YOU LOOK LIKE
RUM TUM TUGGER.
YEAH.

06:53.280 --> 06:55.115
CESAR AND I HAVE A RAPPORT.

06:55.148 --> 06:58.585
HE'S GOT HIS ICY STARE.
I'VE GOT MY MELTY EYES.

06:58.619 --> 07:00.120
EH, WE'RE FRENEMIES.

07:00.153 --> 07:01.788
JUST WHAT IF?
WHAT IF?

07:01.822 --> 07:04.958
I'M NOT SAYING WE ACTUALLY
DO IT. I'M JUST SAYING WHAT IF.

07:04.992 --> 07:06.360
'CAUSE THINK ABOUT IT.

07:06.393 --> 07:08.795
I COULD GO TO COLLEGE,
GET A DEGREE.

07:08.829 --> 07:10.397
SHANE COULD...

07:10.430 --> 07:13.233
I DON'T KNOW, BECOME ONE
OF THOSE GOOD SERIAL KILLERS

07:13.267 --> 07:16.603
WHO ONLY KILLS
OTHER SERIAL KILLERS.

07:16.637 --> 07:18.539
OKAY.

07:18.572 --> 07:20.541
NO, I'M LISTENING.

07:20.574 --> 07:23.877
WHAT WOULD BE SO TERRIBLE?
HYPOTHETICALLY.

07:23.911 --> 07:26.914
PARALLEL UNIVERSE.
A BOY AND HIS FATHER.

07:26.947 --> 07:28.582
WE COULD STOP RUNNING.

07:28.615 --> 07:29.750
STEVIE'S YOUR BROTHER.

07:29.783 --> 07:31.385
STEVIE'S A TIME BOMB.

07:33.153 --> 07:34.588
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

07:34.621 --> 07:36.023
OKAY,
I CAN DO THIS, NANCE.

07:36.056 --> 07:37.291
YOU'RE DROPPING ME OFF.

07:37.324 --> 07:39.293
YOU'RE GONNA FIND
A‐A PUBLIC, CROWDED RESTAURANT.

07:39.326 --> 07:41.929
YOU'RE GONNA WAIT THERE.
YOU'RE GONNA EAT SOMETHING.

07:41.962 --> 07:43.530
WELL,
AT LEAST TAKE THE CAR.

07:43.564 --> 07:45.966
YOU'RE TAKING THE CAR.
KEEP A DISTANCE.

07:45.999 --> 07:47.201
STAY...SAFE.

07:47.234 --> 07:48.035
[ BEEP ]

07:48.068 --> 07:51.238
CESAR:
There's a museum up ahead.

08:18.699 --> 08:21.869
HOLA, CESAR.
vCOMO ESTA?

08:21.902 --> 08:23.737
YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU'VE LOST WEIGHT.

08:23.770 --> 08:27.074
PUT THE BABY DOWN
AND STEP BACK.

08:27.107 --> 08:29.810
NO, NO.
HE'S SLEEPING.

08:29.843 --> 08:31.745
WHERE'S MY SON?

08:33.113 --> 08:35.282
ONE SHOE AT A TIME.

08:36.717 --> 08:39.186
[ GROANING ]

08:42.089 --> 08:44.057
I'M ‐‐ I'M SORRY
ABOUT THAT,

08:44.091 --> 08:47.327
BUT I KNOW
YOU WERE GONNA SHOOT ME FIRST.

08:47.361 --> 08:48.629
SHANE!

08:48.662 --> 08:51.064
SHANE!

08:51.098 --> 08:53.567
IF YOU CAN'T TALK,
KICK SOMETHING!

08:53.600 --> 08:56.470
MAKE A SOUND!

08:56.503 --> 08:58.038
[ SIGHS ]

08:58.071 --> 09:00.407
WHERE IS HE?

09:05.612 --> 09:08.916
I'M A SINEWY BEAST.
VERY BACKUP WORTHY.

09:08.949 --> 09:11.518
WHAT DO YOU THINK
SHE'S DOING?

09:11.552 --> 09:13.153
NEGOTIATING.

09:13.187 --> 09:16.056
IT'S BEEN 10 MINUTES.
I'M STARTING TO FEEL PANICKY.

09:16.089 --> 09:17.891
SHE'S A LONE WOLF.
ALWAYS HAS BEEN.

09:17.925 --> 09:19.193
NOTHING WE CAN DO
ABOUT IT.

09:19.226 --> 09:21.161
WELL, WE CAN'T DO
ANYTHING HERE.

09:21.195 --> 09:23.197
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

09:23.230 --> 09:25.032
WHAT IS IT?
WHAT IS IT?

09:25.065 --> 09:28.135
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]
KIMMI SENT ME HER BOOBS.

09:29.002 --> 09:30.771
WOWSER.

09:30.804 --> 09:31.805
HEY.
OH, SORRY.

09:31.839 --> 09:33.740
AAH, LET'S GO.

09:33.774 --> 09:36.043
SHANE'S OUR SHANE, TOO.
WE DON'T ALWAYS HAVE TO DO
EVERYTHING SHE SAYS.

09:36.076 --> 09:39.146
WE'RE TEAM NEWMAN.
WE COULD HIDE IN THE BUSHES.
SHE WOULDN'T HAVE TO KNOW.

09:39.179 --> 09:42.783
BUT WE'D BE HER INSURANCE ‐‐
JUST IN CASE.

09:42.816 --> 09:43.984
YEAH, RIGHT AFTER WE EAT.

09:44.017 --> 09:46.653
'CAUSE WE'LL BE USELESS
ON AN EMPTY STOMACH.

09:46.687 --> 09:48.989
COFFEE?

09:50.557 --> 09:51.758
FILL HER UP.

09:51.792 --> 09:54.428
ACTUALLY, I'M TRYING TO DECIDE
BETWEEN THE TILAPIA TORPEDOS

09:54.461 --> 09:56.263
AND THE MEAT‐LOVERS
MOOSE TRACKS ‐‐

09:56.296 --> 09:57.898
THE ENTRéE SIZE, NOT THE APP.

09:57.931 --> 09:59.333
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

09:59.366 --> 10:02.002
COME ON, MAN. I'VE HAD NOTHING
TO EAT IN THREE DAYS

10:02.035 --> 10:03.470
EXCEPT
FOR A LINTY‐CAR FRENCH FRY.

10:03.504 --> 10:05.339
HE'S ON A DIET.

10:05.372 --> 10:07.040
THAT'S NOT COOL.

10:07.074 --> 10:08.308
Waitress:
I TRIED THE ONE

10:08.342 --> 10:10.944
WHERE YOU ONLY EAT COTTON BALLS
SOAKED IN GELATIN.

10:10.978 --> 10:13.347
I LOST 6 POUNDS,
BUT IT KILLED THE FETUS.

10:14.681 --> 10:15.782
COFFEE?

10:15.816 --> 10:16.817
BLACK.

10:16.850 --> 10:18.085
AND YOU?

10:18.118 --> 10:20.554
CREAM AND SUGAR.

10:20.587 --> 10:22.189
WOW, THAT'S CUTE.

10:22.222 --> 10:24.625
IT'S HOW I USED TO DRINK IT
WHEN I WAS A KID.

10:24.658 --> 10:26.960
[ CHUCKLES SARCASTICALLY ]

10:26.994 --> 10:28.762
EMPTY YOUR POCKETS.

10:29.997 --> 10:32.499
COME ON.
GIVE ME YOUR KEYS.

10:35.035 --> 10:37.571
I KNOW WHERE HE IS.

10:43.510 --> 10:45.279
[ SIGHS ]

10:45.312 --> 10:47.447
[ DIALING ]

10:47.481 --> 10:49.917
[ Cellphone ringing ]

10:49.950 --> 10:52.152
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

10:55.989 --> 10:59.826
HELLO?
SHANE'S PHONE.

10:59.860 --> 11:01.128
WHAT IS UP?

11:01.161 --> 11:03.764
GIVE ME THAT.
GIVE ME HIS PHONE.

11:04.998 --> 11:08.235
THAT WAS BRATTY.

11:10.771 --> 11:13.273
WHAT IS THAT?
WHAT'S IN YOUR HAND?

11:13.307 --> 11:14.942
NOTHING.

11:14.975 --> 11:16.276
DROP IT.

11:17.411 --> 11:19.279
[ CLINKS ]

11:21.548 --> 11:24.451
[ BEEPING ]
MALE VOICE:
You are a champion!

11:24.484 --> 11:26.954
SERIOUSLY?

11:26.987 --> 11:29.022
I HAVE A MEAN FASTBALL.

11:29.056 --> 11:30.891
GIVE ME YOUR PHONE.

11:30.924 --> 11:32.693
GIVE IT!

11:32.726 --> 11:34.494
AAH!

11:36.763 --> 11:39.299
WHO ‐‐
WHO ARE YOU CALLING?

11:39.333 --> 11:41.134
[ Ringing ]

11:41.168 --> 11:42.536
ESTEBAN:
Sí, Cesar?

11:42.569 --> 11:44.071
OH, WOW.
ESTEBAN.

11:44.104 --> 11:45.405
HI. I DIDN'T ‐‐

11:45.439 --> 11:46.607
[ Click ]

11:48.775 --> 11:51.011
HOW DID THAT GO?

11:52.312 --> 11:55.382
ARE YOU EATING
YOUR NAPKIN?

11:55.415 --> 11:57.618
NO.

11:57.651 --> 11:59.052
OKAY, FINE.

11:59.086 --> 12:02.055
YOU CAN EAT PACKETS
OF ARTIFICIAL SWEETENER.

12:02.089 --> 12:04.424
GOT TO BE INSANE TO EAT
THAT SHIT. IT'S RAT CANCER.

12:04.458 --> 12:06.226
IT'LL TURNS YOUR BLADDER
INTO A SQUISHY PIT,

12:06.260 --> 12:09.930
AND IT'LL SLOWLY AND PAINFULLY
SLIDE OUT YOUR SHIT SHAFT.

12:09.963 --> 12:12.933
HAVE IT YOUR WAY.

12:12.966 --> 12:15.969
GOD WANTS ME TO LIVE.

12:16.003 --> 12:17.738
AND I STILL
DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY.

12:17.771 --> 12:19.306
FOR A LOT OF REASONS.

12:22.976 --> 12:24.144
TELL ME ONE.

12:28.148 --> 12:29.917
I NEED TO TAKE A PISS.

12:29.950 --> 12:31.251
[ CHUCKLES ]

12:31.285 --> 12:33.754
FINE.
BUT I'M WATCHING YOU.

12:36.056 --> 12:38.058
STILL GONNA KILL ME?

12:38.091 --> 12:41.428
IT'S NOT UP TO ME,
PEQUEÑO DIABLO.

12:43.497 --> 12:46.166
SO, A CROQUET MALLET...

12:46.200 --> 12:49.069
YOU GET A GOOD BLUDGEON
OUT OF THAT?

12:49.102 --> 12:50.137
DOES THE JOB.

12:50.170 --> 12:52.139
IT'S NOT EASY, HUH,
YOUR FIRST?

12:52.172 --> 12:54.274
IT WASN'T THAT HARD.

12:55.876 --> 12:58.712
MY FIRST
WAS MY STEPDAD.

12:58.745 --> 13:00.247
HIS NAME WAS RAMON.

13:00.280 --> 13:03.050
HE TRAVELED A LOT
FOR WORK.

13:03.083 --> 13:05.819
THINK HE SOLD HATS.
NO ‐‐ SHOES.

13:05.853 --> 13:07.321
NO, I'M PRETTY SURE
IT WAS HATS.

13:07.354 --> 13:10.290
HE WAS FAT.
REALLY FAT.

13:10.324 --> 13:13.193
NOT FUNNY FAT,
BUT <i>FAT.</i>

13:13.227 --> 13:17.164
ONE NIGHT, I COME HOME.
HE ATE MY COOKIES.

13:18.966 --> 13:21.535
SO I SLIT HIS THROAT
WITH MY POCKETKNIFE,

13:21.568 --> 13:23.270
WITH MY NAVAJA.

13:23.303 --> 13:24.872
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:24.905 --> 13:26.306
I'M GLAD
HE DIDN'T BEG.

13:26.340 --> 13:28.976
NOT THAT I GAVE HIM TIME
FOR IT, ANYWAYS.

13:29.009 --> 13:30.777
[ LAUGHS ]

13:30.811 --> 13:33.981
AND AFTERWARDS, I FIND THE
COOKIES. THEY WERE IN MY ROOM.

13:34.014 --> 13:35.716
DID YOU FEEL BAD?

13:35.749 --> 13:37.050
[ SCOFFS ]
NO.

13:37.084 --> 13:39.019
YEAH, ME NEITHER.

13:39.052 --> 13:42.222
THAT WAS FAST.

13:49.897 --> 13:53.534
YOU EVER CLOSE YOUR EYES AND SEE
HER FACE STARING BACK AT YOU?

13:53.567 --> 13:56.036
ONLY WHEN I JERK OFF.

13:58.138 --> 14:01.508
I'VE HAD PLAYING CARDS
SHOVED UNDER MY FINGERNAILS.

14:01.542 --> 14:04.811
I'VE HAD A PIECE OF MY EAR
CUT OFF AND REATTACHED.

14:04.845 --> 14:06.914
AND THREE COLOMBIANS
ONCE TOOK TURNS

14:06.947 --> 14:10.150
SHOOTING GASOLINE UP MY CULO
WITH A TURKEY BASTER.

14:10.184 --> 14:13.020
SO NOTHING YOU CAN SAY OR DO
WILL MAKE ME TALK.

14:13.053 --> 14:15.989
HI. HI,
IS YOUR MOMMY HOME?

14:17.157 --> 14:20.027
[ <i>WOMAN SPEAKING SPANISH</i>
<i>ON TV</i>]

14:22.930 --> 14:23.997
[ Ringing ]

14:24.031 --> 14:25.832
IT'S RINGING,
BUT SHE'S NOT PICKING UP.

14:25.866 --> 14:27.234
MAYBE SHE'S TRYING
TO CALL US.

14:27.267 --> 14:28.435
YEAH. WE SHOULD KEEP
THE LINES FREE.

14:28.468 --> 14:30.504
YEAH.

14:30.537 --> 14:31.939
[ SIGHS ]

14:31.972 --> 14:33.207
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:33.240 --> 14:35.843
I GOT TO CALL THIS GIRL
BEFORE SHE FREAKS OUT.

14:35.876 --> 14:37.010
HEY.

14:37.044 --> 14:38.812
TRAFFIC'S A MESS.

14:38.846 --> 14:40.080
AND, UM, I THINK THERE ‐‐

14:40.113 --> 14:42.049
THERE MUST BE A MARINERS GAME
OR SOMETHING.

14:42.082 --> 14:46.587
BUT I'M ‐‐ I'M GONNA BE THERE
IN A BIT FOR SURE.

14:46.620 --> 14:48.956
OKAY.

14:48.989 --> 14:50.090
[ BEEP ]

14:50.123 --> 14:52.759
WHERE THE HECK
IS MY FRENCH TOAST?!

14:59.666 --> 15:01.368
[ GASPS ]

15:05.272 --> 15:06.707
[ GRUNTING ]

15:06.740 --> 15:07.908
[ LAUGHS ]

15:07.941 --> 15:09.877
AND WE'RE DEAD.

15:09.910 --> 15:11.011
WHAT'S YOUR LAST NAME?

15:11.044 --> 15:13.847
I DON'T REMEMBER.
SO, WHAT IS IT?

15:13.881 --> 15:15.916
DE LA CRUZ.
DE LA CRUZ.

15:15.949 --> 15:17.117
HI, MRS. DE LA CRUZ.

15:17.150 --> 15:20.454
IT'S, UM, IT'S NANCY...REYES,
ESTEBAN'S WIFE.

15:20.487 --> 15:23.824
Yes! Hi. How are you?
How's the villa?

15:23.857 --> 15:24.858
Uh, it's good.
It's good.

15:24.892 --> 15:27.160
ESTA BIEN.
UM, LISTEN ‐‐

15:33.734 --> 15:35.569
SORRY. GO ON.

15:35.602 --> 15:36.537
Um...

15:36.570 --> 15:38.405
I KNOW THAT CESAR
MIGHT NOT SHARE WITH YOU

15:38.438 --> 15:39.940
EVERYTHING
THAT HAPPENS AT WORK,

15:39.973 --> 15:43.143
BUT TODAY,
HE KIDNAPPED MY SON.

15:43.177 --> 15:44.811
AND NOW HE'S THREATENING
TO KILL HIM.

15:44.845 --> 15:46.280
TELL HER
ABOUT THE ARROW.

15:53.353 --> 15:55.022
Mrs. ‐‐ Mrs. De La Cruz?
HMM?

15:55.055 --> 15:57.958
I‐I WAS JUST WONDERING
IF YOU ‐‐ YOU COULD TALK TO HIM,

15:57.991 --> 15:59.660
YOU KNOW, AS ANOTHER MOTHER.

15:59.693 --> 16:01.361
I see.
Is he there?

16:01.395 --> 16:04.431
YOU LET ME TALK TO HIM.
Yeah, he's right here.
Okay.

16:04.464 --> 16:07.167
HERE, TALK ‐‐ TALK TO HER.
SHE WANTS TO TALK TO YOU.

16:10.571 --> 16:11.738
Sí.

16:11.772 --> 16:13.540
Sí.

16:13.574 --> 16:15.709
BUENO.

16:15.742 --> 16:17.878
WHAT DID SHE SAY?

16:17.911 --> 16:20.914
SHE SAID TO KILL YOU
AND COME HOME.

16:20.948 --> 16:23.951
SHE'S MAKING ALBóNDIGAS
FOR DINNER.

16:23.984 --> 16:26.687
[ SIGHS ]

16:26.720 --> 16:27.754
[ THUD ]

16:29.056 --> 16:31.825
[ BEEPING ]
MALE VOICE:
You are a champion!

16:31.859 --> 16:34.094
[ BEEPING CONTINUES ]

16:34.127 --> 16:37.030
[ UP‐TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS
IN BACKGROUND ]

16:54.381 --> 16:56.216
[ Whispering loudly ]
Pittsburgh!

16:58.051 --> 16:59.186
Pittsburgh!

17:02.256 --> 17:03.857
[ Coughing ]
SAMMY DAVIS, JR.!

17:03.891 --> 17:05.392
Fuck.

17:06.426 --> 17:09.363
NOT THE ASHTRAY.

17:19.806 --> 17:21.208
AH.

17:21.241 --> 17:23.310
MAYBE ‐‐ MAYBE
WE SHOULD CALL MOM AGAIN.

17:23.343 --> 17:25.712
I CAN DO THIS.
YOU DON'T THINK I CAN DO THIS?

17:34.354 --> 17:35.622
[ SIGHS ]

17:38.959 --> 17:40.561
OKAY.

17:40.594 --> 17:42.496
I'M GOIN' IN.

17:42.529 --> 17:43.797
THIS TIME, NO BROOM.

17:43.830 --> 17:47.034
JUST FISTS, SINEW,
ANDY‐MEAT.

17:47.067 --> 17:49.036
WHATEVER HAPPENS,
DON'T TRY TO SAVE ME.

17:49.069 --> 17:51.205
ARE YOU SURE?
NO.

17:57.978 --> 17:59.179
[ GRUNTS ]

18:00.013 --> 18:00.981
[ SNEEZES ]

18:01.014 --> 18:02.015
BLESS YOU.

18:02.049 --> 18:04.051
SIT DOWN, PLEASE.
OKEYDOKE.

18:04.084 --> 18:08.021
AND, YOU...
BRING THE LITTLE ONE.

18:10.457 --> 18:13.927
HEY, SILAS.

18:13.961 --> 18:16.230
SILAS. WHAT'S UP?

18:16.263 --> 18:19.266
OH, HEY, THERE.
YOUR FRENCH TOAST IS READY.

18:19.299 --> 18:21.835
OR DID YOU WANT TO EAT
WITH YOUR FRIENDS?

18:21.869 --> 18:23.470
YEAH.

18:28.775 --> 18:31.411
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

18:31.445 --> 18:32.212
CESAR.

18:32.246 --> 18:35.382
[ GROANS ]
CESAR! CESAR!

18:35.415 --> 18:38.118
OH.

18:38.151 --> 18:39.720
I'M ‐‐ I'M GONNA PUT YOU
ON SPEAKERPHONE.

18:39.753 --> 18:43.023
BE GOOD, AND I'LL ‐‐ I'LL CALL
YOU AN AMBULANCE, OKAY?

18:43.056 --> 18:44.358
ENGLISH PREFERRED.

18:44.391 --> 18:46.426
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA BE SAFE,
YOU KNOW.

18:46.460 --> 18:47.561
ANSWER IT.

18:47.594 --> 18:48.462
HELLO?

18:48.495 --> 18:50.831
IGNACIO:
Everyone, say hi to Cesar.

18:50.864 --> 18:52.299
ANDY, DOUG, SILAS:
Hi, Cesar.

18:52.332 --> 18:54.134
IGNACIO:
Man, come pick me up.

18:54.168 --> 18:56.236
You never guess who I found.

18:56.270 --> 18:58.071
[ CLICK ]
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

19:11.151 --> 19:14.121
COME ON, CESAR.
WHERE ARE YOU?

19:14.154 --> 19:15.522
DRIVES LIKE
MY GRANDMOTHER.

19:15.556 --> 19:18.458
ON HER LEFT HAND,
SHE GOT TWO RING FINGERS.

19:18.492 --> 19:20.627
HOW DOES THAT AFFECT
HER DRIVING?

19:20.661 --> 19:22.062
IT'S JUST A FUN FACT.

19:22.095 --> 19:24.431
MAYBE HE'S HAVING TROUBLE
GETTING MOM INTO THE TRUNK.

19:24.464 --> 19:26.033
[ CHUCKLES ]

19:27.801 --> 19:30.938
SHANE.
MY SON.

19:30.971 --> 19:34.241
AND HE FED YOU ‐‐
NACHOS.

19:34.274 --> 19:36.543
YUM!

19:36.577 --> 19:39.279
[ SIGHS ]

19:39.313 --> 19:42.583
I FEEL ‐‐
I FEEL SO...

19:42.616 --> 19:43.784
MOM, ARE YOU OKAY?

19:43.817 --> 19:44.918
WHERE'S CESAR?

19:44.952 --> 19:46.353
UM...

19:46.386 --> 19:49.990
CESAR.
YOU SHOULD'VE SEEN ME.
I WAS HEROIC.

19:50.023 --> 19:51.258
CESAR HAD
AN ACCIDENT.

19:51.291 --> 19:53.227
HE'S IN THE HOSPITAL.
YOU SHOULD GO AND VISIT HIM.

19:53.260 --> 19:55.662
SO, NOW I'M GOING TO TAKE
MY SHANE AND MY STEVIE,

19:55.696 --> 19:56.997
AND I'LL BE GOING.

19:57.030 --> 19:59.967
WE'LL ALL BE GOING.
DOUG, YOU CAN COME, TOO.

20:00.000 --> 20:01.969
YOU ALL RIGHT THERE,
DOUG?

20:02.002 --> 20:05.138
THERE'S THIS STUPID KID.
HE'S SUCH A FUCKING JERK.

20:06.573 --> 20:08.342
AH.

20:09.409 --> 20:12.813
I HAVE A GUN
POINTED AT YOUR SCROTUM.

20:12.846 --> 20:13.981
WELL...

20:14.014 --> 20:17.417
I HAVE A GUN POINTING
AT YOUR LADY SCROTUM.

20:20.988 --> 20:22.089
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

20:22.122 --> 20:24.892
UH, NOTHING.
WATER.

20:24.925 --> 20:26.026
LEMON WEDGE?

20:26.059 --> 20:28.996
UH, NO.
WATER. ICE.

20:29.029 --> 20:30.664
UH, WE'RE OUT OF ICE.

20:30.697 --> 20:31.932
HOW CAN YOU BE
OUT OF ICE?

20:31.965 --> 20:33.267
THE ICE MACHINE BROKE.

20:33.300 --> 20:35.702
OKAY, THEN LEMON.
SO, NO WATER?

20:35.736 --> 20:39.540
I'LL HAVE A STEAK SANDWICH.
SIDE SALAD. STRAWBERRY SHAKE.

20:39.573 --> 20:41.608
DOUG,
NOT THE TIME.

20:45.412 --> 20:46.313
Doug?

20:46.346 --> 20:49.082
Nancy: COME ON, IGNACIO,
YOU REALLY THINK

20:49.116 --> 20:51.585
YOU CAN SUCCESSFULLY TRANSPORT
AN INFANT

20:51.618 --> 20:53.120
2,000 MILES
BY YOURSELF?

20:53.153 --> 20:54.354
Sí.

20:54.388 --> 20:57.024
WHAT EXACTLY DOES
A 3‐MONTH‐OLD EAT?

20:57.057 --> 20:59.326
CHICKEN. CRACKERS.

20:59.359 --> 21:01.094
INCORRECT.

21:01.128 --> 21:05.299
WELL, MAYBE
YOU COME WITH ME.

21:05.332 --> 21:08.669
WE BOTH KNOW
THAT'S NOT GONNA HAPPEN.

21:11.839 --> 21:14.041
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:16.810 --> 21:18.812
YOUR HANDS ARE SHAKING.

21:18.846 --> 21:20.848
YOU'RE NOT GONNA SHOOT ME.

21:20.881 --> 21:22.616
I WILL.

21:22.649 --> 21:23.851
NO.

21:23.884 --> 21:25.819
I COULD.

21:25.853 --> 21:28.021
DON'T GET ME WRONG.
YOU'RE A TOUGHIE.

21:28.055 --> 21:29.923
BUT THIS...
[ TAPS ]

21:29.957 --> 21:31.024
NO.

21:31.058 --> 21:34.494
SO, WHY DON'T WE DISCUSS
A LITTLE MORE

21:34.528 --> 21:36.029
ABOUT OUR PLANS?

21:36.063 --> 21:38.198
HE'S RIGHT.
YOU'RE NOT GONNA SHOOT HIM.

21:38.232 --> 21:41.568
I WILL IF I HAVE TO.
BUT YOU DON'T HAVE TO.

21:46.406 --> 21:48.976
YOU GONNA PUT A BULLET
IN ME, MIJO?

21:49.009 --> 21:50.377
[ GUN COCKS ]

21:50.410 --> 21:52.746
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

22:02.923 --> 22:05.559
FOLLOW YOUR DREAMS,
MIJO.

22:12.966 --> 22:15.235
FOLLOW YOUR DREAMS.

22:15.269 --> 22:21.208
♪♪ I WILL DREAM
OF SUNNY SKIES OF BLUE ♪♪

22:21.241 --> 22:23.810
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

22:23.844 --> 22:25.279
[ HORN HONKS ]

22:32.819 --> 22:35.689
HEY, IT'S ME.

22:35.722 --> 22:37.057
YEAH...

22:37.090 --> 22:40.827
YOUR CAR GOT STOLEN.

22:40.861 --> 22:43.230
ALSO, I THINK
WE SHOULD SEE OTHER PEOPLE.

22:43.263 --> 22:46.099
FEMALE VOICE: You have reached
the voice mailbox of...

22:46.133 --> 22:47.234
ESTEBAN: Esteban.

22:47.267 --> 22:48.902
FEMALE VOICE:
Please record your message.

22:48.936 --> 22:50.938
[ Beep ]
HI. IT'S CESAR.

22:50.971 --> 22:52.806
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:52.840 --> 22:54.007
JUST KIDDING.

22:54.041 --> 22:57.544
UM, DON'T BE MAD AT HIM.
YOU KNOW?

22:57.578 --> 23:00.314
I'M A ‐‐ I'M A MOTHER LION.

23:00.347 --> 23:07.287
AND YOU CAN'T DEFEAT A MOTHER
LION WHEN YOU THREATEN HER CUBS.

23:07.321 --> 23:10.023
YOU MIGHT THINK IT'S
THE SAME THING FOR PAPA LION,

23:10.057 --> 23:11.925
BUT IT'S NOT.

23:11.959 --> 23:14.661
IT'S NOT THE SAME THING
AT ALL.

23:14.695 --> 23:20.033
ESTEBAN,
I WANT TO THANK YOU

23:20.067 --> 23:22.903
FOR OUR BEAUTIFUL BOY.

23:22.936 --> 23:26.874
BUT, UM,
I HAVE TO DISAPPEAR NOW.

23:26.907 --> 23:30.511
I WILL ALWAYS SPEAK WELL OF YOU

23:30.544 --> 23:34.081
AND I‐I'LL ALWAYS TELL HIM
HOW MUCH I LOVED HIS FATHER

23:34.114 --> 23:39.920
AND HOW SO, SO FOND OF YOU
I ONCE WAS.

23:39.953 --> 23:41.255
[ SNIFFLES ]

23:41.288 --> 23:44.992
YOU'RE GONNA MISS STEVIE,
AND I'M SO SORRY FOR THAT.

23:45.025 --> 23:48.795
BUT HE NEEDS ME ALIVE
MORE THAN HE NEEDS ME DEAD.

23:48.829 --> 23:50.931
SHOCKER ‐‐ I KNOW.

23:50.964 --> 23:53.467
AGAIN, IT ‐‐ IT ‐‐
IT HURTS YOU, I KNOW.

23:53.500 --> 23:56.270
AND I'M ‐‐ I'M SORRY,
BUT I'M THE MOM.

23:56.303 --> 23:59.706
AND...
HE NEEDS ME MORE, SO...

23:59.740 --> 24:05.913
OH, UM, CESAR'S ALIVE,
BY THE WAY, IF THAT WAS UNCLEAR.

24:05.946 --> 24:07.014
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

24:07.047 --> 24:08.982
SO, UM...

24:09.016 --> 24:13.453
GOOD LUCK
WITH YOUR CRIME AND STUFF.

24:13.487 --> 24:16.223
OKAY. BYE.

24:17.291 --> 24:19.059
UNA NAVAJA.

24:19.092 --> 24:21.662
OH, SHANE, SHANE...

24:21.695 --> 24:23.997
NO MORE SPANISH.

24:24.031 --> 24:27.334
♪♪ I'M MAKING MY WAY ♪♪

24:27.367 --> 24:30.737
♪♪ YEAH, I'M MOVING ON ♪♪

24:30.771 --> 24:33.507
♪♪ GOT TO, GOT TO GET AWAY ♪♪

24:33.540 --> 24:37.811
♪♪ NO MAS, NO MAS ♪♪

24:37.845 --> 24:39.847
♪♪ NOW GO ♪♪

24:39.880 --> 24:43.984
♪♪ I THINK YOUR DEFINITION
